Conversions to supported formats inside the EPUB
 * bitmaps to jpg or png.
 * wmf/emf/svm to svg

Frames
 * Different anchor and text run-around cases
 * Get replacement images from content shapes that we
   don't recognize.

Conversions to supported formats inside the EPUB
 * Convert wmf to svg
 * Convert emf to svg
 * Convert svm to svg

More formatting
 * Space before/after a paragraph



